msgstr "Haƙiƙa, wannan alama ta na wakiltar Mai gewayawa ta Firefox."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"That’s right. This customer seems like a Firefox fan. Talk about how the "
"Firefox OS phones, made by Mozilla, show a commitment to keeping the power "
"of the Web in the hands of the people. And while all of these statements are"
" true, only this one is the best response for this particular customer."
msgstr ""
"Ya yi dai dai. Wannan abokin cinikin kamar abokin Firefox OS ne. Tattauna a "
"kan yadda wayoyin Firefox OS, da Mozilla suka yi, nuna dukufa ta ajiye "
"ƙarfin Yanar gizo a hannun waɗan nan mutane. Yayin da duk waɗan nan "
"maganganu suke dai dai, wannan ce kawai amsa mafi inganci ga wannan abokin "
"cinikin."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Share contacts"
msgstr "Raba abokan hulɗa"

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"If you’ve worked through all of the questions and content, you’re ready to "
"match Firefox OS to the needs of your customers.  Easy to use, a Firefox OS "
"smartphone is perfect for new smartphone users and full of all the features "
"that customers want and need.  And it’s powered by Mozilla, making Firefox "
"OS the right choice for anyone committed to ensuring that the power of the "
"Web remains in their hands!"
msgstr ""
"Idan ka duba duk tambayoyi da abin da ke ciki, ka shirya haɗa Firefox OS da "
"bukatun abokan cinikinka.  Sauƙin amfani, babbar wayar Firefox OS ta dace da"
" sababbin masu amfani da babbar waya kuma cike da siffofin da mai amafi ke "
"nema da bukata.  Kuma ƙarfafawa daga Mozilla, ya mayar da Firefox OS zaɓin "
"da ya fi dacewa ga duk wanda ya dukufa domin tabbatar da ƙarfin Yanar gizo "
"ya tabbata a hannunsu!"

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"What’s the best response to this customer’s objection? “I’ve heard there "
"aren’t many apps available.”"
msgstr ""
"Mece ce amsa mafi dacewa ga batun wannan mai ciniki? “Na ji cewa babu "
"aikace-aikace da yawa.”"

#: 2-0/customer-guide/ 1-3/customer-guide/ 2-1/customer-guide/
msgid ""
"<strong>Here’s what you can say:</strong> Firefox OS is the best choice for "
"first time smartphone users. It’s super easy to use and adapts to your needs"
" better than any other phone. That means you get more of what you need with "
"less time spent searching. Plus, it’s packed with all the features you’d "
"expect — camera, email, apps, music, maps and more!"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ga abin da za ka ce:</strong> Firefox OS ita ce kyakkyawan zaɓi ga "
"wanda ya fara amfani da babbar waya a karon farko. Ta na da matuƙar sauƙi "
"kuma na iya dacewa da bukatunka fiye da ko wace irin waya. Wannan na nufin "
"zaka sami duk abin da ka ke bukata cikin lokaci kaɗan na nema. Kuma, an "
"cikata da siffofi da ka ke zato — kyamara, imel, aikace-aikace, kiɗa, "
"taswirori da sauransu!"

#: 2-0/customer-guide/ 1-3/customer-guide/ 2-1/customer-guide/
msgid ""
"Understanding your customer’s needs and knowing how to respond on the spot "
"is critical to any sales opportunity. Check out the common customer segments"
" below to learn how to best respond to each of their unique needs."
msgstr ""
"Fahimtar bukatar abokan cinikinka da kuma sanin yadda za ka bayar da amsa a "
"nan take na da mahimmanci wajen ko wace dama ta sayarwa. Duba kashe-kashen "
"abokan hulɗa a ƙasa domin koyon ta yadda za ka bayar da amsa ga mabambantan "
"bukatunsu."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"They’re new and backed by a global community working to help keep the Web "
"accessible to all."
msgstr ""
"Sababbi ne kuma su na da goyon bayan al'umma ta duniya masu aiki domin "
"tabbatar da samun dama ga Yanar gizo ga kowa."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"What’s the best response to this customer’s objection? “I’ve never heard of "
"Firefox OS phones.\""
msgstr ""
"Mece ce amsa mafi dacewa ga batun wannan mai ciniki? “Ban taɓa ji ba game da"
" wayoyin Firefox OS.\""

#: 2-0/frequently-asked-questions/ 1-3/frequently-asked-questions/
#: 2-1/frequently-asked-questions/
msgid "Will my apps work offline?"
msgstr "Aikace-aikacena za su yi aiki ko ba haɗin yanar gizo?"

#: 2-0/key-features/ 1-3/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid ""
"Stay connected easily and conveniently. Set up multiple email accounts, with"
" support for the most common Exchange, POP3 or IMAP email providers."
msgstr ""
"Zama cikin haɗi a sauƙaƙe da dacewa. Saita asusun imel masu yawa, tare da "
"tallafi domin Musanya da abubuwa game-gari, POP3 ko IMAP masu bayar da imel."

#: 2-0/introduction/ 1-3/introduction/ 2-1/introduction/
msgid ""
"Life is complicated, your smartphone shouldn’t be. Firefox OS is designed "
"for better performance, easier customization and simpler navigation. "
"Everything your customer needs or wants is either one scroll or swipe away."
msgstr ""
"Rayuwa na da rikici, babbar wayarka bai kamata ta zama haka ba. An shirya "
"Firefox OS domin ingantaccen aiki, tsarawa mai sauƙi da gewayawa mai sauƙi. "
"Duk abin da mai ciniki ya ke so ko bukata ko dai gungurawa ɗaya ko kuma "
"matsawa."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Actually, all of these are true about Firefox OS."
msgstr "Haƙiƙa, duk waɗan nan gaskiya ne dangane da Firefox OS."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"Firefox OS is backed by a global community of developers and content "
"providers dedicated to creating new and exciting content and even locally-"
"relevant apps for the Firefox OS platform. New apps and content are added "
"every day."
msgstr ""
"Firefox OS na da goyon bayan al'umma ta duniya na masu samarwa da masu samar"
" da abubuwan ciki da suka dukufa domin ƙirƙirar sabo kuma kyakkyawan abin "
"ciki da ko da aikace-aikace na gida domin dandalin Firefox OS. Sababbin "
"aikace-aikace da abin ciki ana ƙarasu a kullum."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"That’s right! All of these things are possible with a Firefox OS phone."
msgstr ""
"Ya yi dai dai! Duk waɗannan abubuwa na iya yiwuwa tare da wayar Firefox OS."

#: 2-0/frequently-asked-questions/ 1-3/frequently-asked-questions/
#: 2-1/frequently-asked-questions/
msgid "Exchange, POP3 and IMAP are currently supported."
msgstr "Sauya, POP3 da IMAP yanzu su na da tallafi."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "There are more. Try again."
msgstr "Akwai saura. Sake gwadawa."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"Actually, when you meet a Firefox fan, talk about how choosing Firefox OS "
"shows a commitment to keeping power of the the Web in their hands."
msgstr ""
"A haƙiƙa, idan ka haɗu da abokin Firefox, ya magana a kan yadda zaɓar "
"Firefox OS ya nuna dukufa ta tabbatar da ƙarfin Yanar gizo a hannunsu."

#: 2-0/demo-tips/ 1-3/demo-tips/ 2-1/demo-tips/
msgid ""
"Firefox OS comes preloaded with popular instant messaging and social media "
"apps, like Facebook, so your customers will be able to stay connected with "
"friends and family. They can also sync their contacts to the phone, quickly "
"and easily."
msgstr ""
"Firefox OS ta zo an loda mata fitattun aikace-aikace na aikawa da saƙo da "
"dandalin sa-da-zumunta kamar Facebook, ta yadda abokan cinikinka za su sami "
"haɗi da abokai da dangi. Kuma za su iya tsara abokan hulɗarsu zuwa wayar, "
"cikin sauri da sauƙi."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Share images"
msgstr "Raba hotuna"

#: 2-0/key-features/ 1-3/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid ""
"Your go-to source for the best apps on Firefox OS. Browse multiple "
"categories, including games, utilities, music, travel, sports and more."
msgstr ""
"Ka tafi zuwa tushe domin mafi kyau na aikace-aikace a kan Firefox OS. Gewaya"
" ga kashe-kashe masu yawa, da suka haɗa da wasanni, kayayyaki, kiɗa, tafiye-"
"tafiye, wasanni da sauransu."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "That’s right. This icon represents the Firefox Browser."
msgstr "Ya yi dai dai. Wannan alama ta na wakiltar Mai Gewayawa ta Firefox."

#: 2-0/introduction/ 1-3/introduction/ 2-1/introduction/
msgid "Keep the Web in your hands"
msgstr "Riƙe Yanar gizo a hannunka"

#: 2-0/frequently-asked-questions/ 1-3/frequently-asked-questions/
#: 2-1/frequently-asked-questions/
msgid ""
"Firefox Marketplace is our go-to source for free apps, including favorites "
"like Twitter and Facebook, and for awesome local content from the best Web "
"developers in your region."
msgstr ""
"Wurin Kasuwanci na Firefox shi ne wurin zuwanmu domin samun aikace-aikace na"
" kyauta, wanda ya haɗa da abubuwan so kamar Twitter da Facebook, da kuma "
"haɗi na gida masu ƙayatarwa daga Yanar gizo mafi kyau a shiyyarka."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"They’re packed with the features that made you want a smartphone in the "
"first place."
msgstr ""
"An cikasu da siffofi waɗanda za su sa ka so babbar wayar hannu tun da farko."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"Mozilla, the maker of Firefox, built a smartphone OS to keep the Web "
"accessible to all. And since Firefox OS is entirely built in HTML5, you get "
"instant access to thousands of apps already built for the Web."
msgstr ""
"Mozilla, masu yin Firefox, sun gina babbar wayar OS domin samun dama ga "
"Yanar gizo ga kowa. Kuma tunda an gina Firefox OS gaba ɗaya a kan tsarin "
"HTML5, zaka sami dama nan take ga dubban aikace-aikace da aka gina domin "
"Yanar gizo."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Set your phone to your language"
msgstr "Saita wayarka zuwa yarenka"

#: 2-0/frequently-asked-questions/ 1-3/frequently-asked-questions/
#: 2-1/frequently-asked-questions/
msgid ""
"Users can place bookmarks to any website on their home screen to provide the"
" functionality of that site directly from there. Also, users can simply "
"enter any search term on the home screen and instantly create a one-time use"
" or downloadable app. Creating and consuming these apps on demand puts users"
" in complete control of their smartphone experience and makes it possible "
"for people to get the exact content they want, when they want it."
msgstr ""
"Masu amfani na iya saka zaunannun alamomi a ko wace yanar gizo a shafinsu na"
" gida domin samar da aiki na wannan tashar gizo daga nan. Kuma, masu amfani "
"na iya shiga cikin sauƙi cikin ko wace irin ƙa'ida ta nema a kan fuskar "
"kwamfuta ta shafin gida kuma nan take su ƙirƙiri amfani na lokaci guda ko "
"aikace-aikace wanda za'a iya saukewa. Ƙirƙira da kuma yin amfani da aikace-"
"aikace a lokacin da aka nema ya saka masu amfani a cikakkiyar sarrafawa na "
"koyon da suke da shi na wayar hannu kuma ya sa yiwuwar mutane su sami bayani"
" na haƙiƙa da su ke nema, lokacin da suke nemansa."

#: 2-0/key-features/ 1-3/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid ""
"Easily pair your device with a wide range of Bluetooth accessories. Share "
"contacts, images, videos or your favorite URLs with friends."
msgstr ""
"Cikin sauƙi tagwaita na'urarka da zaɓi mai yawa na kayayyakin Bluetooth. "
"Raba abokan hulɗa, hotuna, bidiyoyi ko URL da ka fi so tare da abokai."

#: 2-0/customer-guide/ 1-3/customer-guide/ 2-1/customer-guide/
msgid ""
"<strong>Here’s what you can say:</strong> If you know and love Firefox, "
"you’ll love Firefox OS.  Firefox OS smartphones are entirely HTML5-based, "
"bringing the best of the Web to your phone.  Plus, Firefox OS is designed by"
" a community dedicated to keeping the Web accessible to all. When you choose"
" Firefox OS, you have the full power of the Web in your hands."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ga abin da za ka ce:</strong> idan ka san kuma ka na son Firefox, za"
" ka so Firefox OS.  Manyan wayoyin Firefox OS dukkansu na da tsarin HTML5, "
"mai kawo mafi kyau na Yanar gizo zuwa wayarka.  Kuma, Firefox OS an tsarata "
"daga jama'a masu mayar da hankali domin ganin Yanar gizo ta isa ga kowa. "
"Idan ka zaɓi Firefox OS, kana da cikakkiyar damar Yanar gizo a hannunka."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"All of these statements are true, but only one is the best response for this"
" particular customer, who seems to be a Firefox fan. Talk about how Firefox "
"OS phones, made by Mozilla, help keep the power of the Web in the hands of "
"the people."
msgstr ""
"Duk waɗan nan maganganun gaskiya ne, amma ɗaya ce amsa mafi inganci ga "
"wannan abokin ciniki, wanda ya zama kamar abokin firefox. Yi magana a kan "
"yadda wayoyin Firefox OS, da Mozilla suka yi, taimaka wajen ajiye ƙarfin "
"Yanar gizo a hannun mutanen."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Firefox OS is built entirely using HTML5 and Open Web standards."
msgstr ""
"An gina Firefox OS gaba ɗaya ta amfani da HTML5 da kuma Buɗaɗɗiyar Yanar "
"Gizo madaidaiciya."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Take the Challenge"
msgstr "Karɓi Ƙalubalen"

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"That’s right. When you meet a Firefox fan, talk about how choosing Firefox "
"OS shows a commitment to keeping the power of the Web in their hands."
msgstr ""
"Ya yi dai dai. Idan ka haɗu da abokin Firefox, yi magana a kan yadda Firefox"
" OS ta maida hankali na ajiye ƙarfin tafiyar da Yanar gizo a hannunsu."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Share videos"
msgstr "Raba bidiyo"

#: 2-0/introduction/ 1-3/introduction/ 2-1/introduction/
msgid ""
"At Mozilla, we’re out to make a difference, not a profit.   Firefox OS "
"smartphones are backed by a global community of developers working to "
"innovate and further Web technologies.    When you choose Firefox OS, you’re"
" helping build a brighter future for the Web for all."
msgstr ""
"A mozilla, mun fito domin mu kawo bambanci, ba riba ba.   Manyan wayoyin "
"Firefox OS na da goyon bayan jama'ar duniya na masu samarwa da suke aiki "
"domin ƙirƙiro da haɓaka fasahar Yanar gizo.    Idan ka zaɓi Firefox OS, kana"
" taimakawa wajen gina gaba kyakkyawa domin Yanar gizo ga kowa."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"It’s packed with the features that made you want a smartphone in the first "
"place."
msgstr ""
"An cikata da siffofi waɗanda za su sa ka so babbar wayar hannu tun da farko."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"It’s new and backed by a global community working to help keep the Web "
"accessible to all."
msgstr ""
"Sabuwa ce kuma mai goyon bayan al'umma ta duniya masu aiki domin taimakawa a"
" bar yanar gizo ta zama samammiya ga kowa."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"That’s right! All of these things can be shared via Bluetooth with your "
"Firefox OS phone."
msgstr ""
"Ya yi dai dai! Duk waɗan nan abubuwa za'a iya rabasu ta hanyar Bluetooth da "
"wayarka ta Firefox OS."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"Apps developers are slowly realizing the benefit of HTML5 in support of the "
"Open Web."
msgstr ""
"Masu samar da aikace-aikace a hankali su na gane amfanin HTML5 wajen "
"tallafwa Buɗaɗɗiyar Yanar gizo."

#: 2-0/key-features/ 1-3/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid ""
"Easily import your Facebook friends to your phone and keep your community "
"all in one place thanks to deep integration with your favorite social "
"networks."
msgstr ""
"Cikin sauƙi ka shigo da abokanka na Facebook zuwa wayarka kuma ka ajiye "
"al'ummarka duk a waje ɗaya godiya da wannan gamayya tare da dandalin sada "
"zumunta wanda ka fi so."

#: 2-0/introduction/ 1-3/introduction/ 2-1/introduction/
msgid ""
"Your customers want to get the most out of life, so why should they get any "
"less from their mobile device?  Firefox OS devices are perfect for new "
"smartphone users — easy to use and full of all the features that they "
"expect. And because Firefox OS devices are powered by Mozilla, they’re the "
"perfect choice for anyone committed to keeping the Web open for all."
msgstr ""
"Abokan cinikinka su na so su sami abubuwa daga rayuwarsu, sabo da haka mai "
"yasa za su sami tawaya daga na'urarsu?  Na'urorin Firefox OS sun dace da "
"sababbin masu amfani da babbar wayar hannu — sauƙin amfani da duk siffofin "
"da su ke tsammani. Kuma sabo da na'urorin Firefox sun sami ƙarfafawar "
"Mozilla, su ne zaɓin da ya fi dacewa ga kowa wanda ya mayar da hankali wajen"
" mayar da Yanar gizo ga kowa."

#: 2-0/key-features/ 1-3/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid ""
"Play it all from your phone, or online via YouTube. Browse and play your "
"music collection by album or artist, rate songs and create playlists for "
"your favorites."
msgstr ""
"Yi wasa da shi duk daga wayraka, ko kuma a kan yanar gizo ta hanyar YouTube."
" Gewaya kuma ka saka waƙarka daga faifai ko mawaƙi, auna waƙoƙi kuma ka "
"ƙirƙiri jerin mawaƙa domin abubuwan da ka fi bukata."

#: 2-0/customer-guide/ 1-3/customer-guide/ 2-1/customer-guide/
msgid ""
"<strong>Here’s what you can say:</strong> Firefox OS is the easiest "
"smartphone to get you started.  The user interface is so intuitive, you’ll "
"be able to quickly discover and download your favorite apps and be ready to "
"go in no time."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ga abin da za ka ce:</strong> Firefox OS ita ce babbar wayar hannu "
"mai sauƙi da za ta sa ka fara.  An yi fasaha wajen samar da yadda mai amfani"
" zai sarrafata, cikin sauri za ka gano kuma ka sauke aikace-aikacenka kuma "
"nan da nan ka fara amfani da su."

#: 2-0/key-features/ 1-3/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid "Bluetooth"
msgstr "Bluetooth"

#: 2-0/demo-tips/ 1-3/demo-tips/ 2-1/demo-tips/
msgid ""
"With Camera, Gallery, Music apps and more, Firefox OS will keep your "
"customers entertained on the go and connected to the things that matter most"
" to them.  <br><br>Camera: Photograph, edit and share. Show off our full-"
"featured camera and gallery apps, including built-in style filters, video "
"and more.  <br><br>Music: With music at their fingertips, your customers "
"will see how Firefox OS keeps them entertained and dancing in the streets."
msgstr ""
"Tare da Kyamara, Ma'ajiyar Hotuna, aikace-aikacen kaɗe-kaɗe da sauransu, "
"Firefox OS za ta ɗebewa abokan cinikinka kewa nan take kuma su haɗa da "
"abubuwan da su ke bukata.  <br><br>Kyamara: Hoto, gyara kuma ka raba. Nunin "
"cikakkiyar siffa ta kyamara da aikace-aikacen hotuna, ya haɗa da rariya "
"wadda aka gina, bidiyo da daɗi.  <br><br>Kiɗa: Tare da kiɗa a tafin "
"hannunka, abokan cinikinka za su kalli yadda Firefox OS za ta ɗebe masu kewa"
" da kuma rawa a kan tituna."

#: 2-0/introduction/ 1-3/introduction/ 2-1/introduction/
msgid "Made with you in mind"
msgstr "An yi ta da kai a zuciya"

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 1-3/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"It features a robust security model that is battle-hardened from more than a"
" decade supporting the Open Web. Designed to protect the user and system "
"from malicious applications and content, it also protects applications from "
